La Veneno https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/La_Veneno 0 Cristina Ortiz Rodríguez (19 March 1964 – 9 November 2016), better known as La Veneno ("Poison"), was a Spanish transsexual vedette, singer and actress. She is better known for appearing in the late-night talk shows Esta noche cruzamos el Mississippi and La sonrisa del pelícano, broadcast between 1996–97 and hosted by journalist Pepe Navarro.
